  including lodging  may be found at the Lexington and Rockbridge Area Tourism site  Hotels offering blocks of room for the conference  from November 2 4  2014  include  Hotel                                                  Rate Per Night                Telephone                          Best Western Inn at Hunt Ridge    83 plus taxes  540  464 1500 Best Western Inn Lexington   83 plus taxes  540   458 3020  Comfort Inn  83 plus taxes  540  463 7311 Holiday Inn Express Lexington  83 plus taxes  540  463 7351 Attendees requiring handicapped accessibility or other assistance are encouraged to contact Mrs  Ronda Dove at  540  464 7361 for information and coordination  VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu 